# Shaman Ovale script based on SimulationCraft profiles
#
# Revision History
# 4.3.1 2011/12/07 - Initial version based on Ovale default script.
#                    Use shaman profiles from SimulationCraft, Tier 13H:
#                        Elemental (r10348), Enhancement (r10526)

## defines ##

